snippet: Jurors in the trial of David Tarloff, who is charged in the 2008 murder of Kathryn Faughey, went home for the weekend after finishing a third day of deliberations.
abstract: Jurors in the trial of David Tarloff, schizophrenic man charged in the 2008 murder of Upper East Side psychologist Kathryn Faughey, finish third day of deliberations without reaching a verdict.
lead_paragraph: Jurors in the trial of David Tarloff, who is charged in the 2008 murder of Kathryn Faughey, went home for the weekend after finishing a third day of deliberations.

headline.seo: Jury to Continue Deliberations in Trial of Psychologist’s Killer
headline.main: Jury Still Out on Killer of Psychologist
headline.print_headline: Jury Still Out on Killer of Psychologist
